{"tid":919192,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我係唔係有濕疹","createTime":"2018-11-28T00:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T03:26:05.000Z","uid":13518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"728206c732ff114f084f8d50327251a86f4fb0e6","tid":919192,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:45:56.000Z","msg":"最近唔知係轉天氣定點 手指頭係咁甩皮<br />\n但係一尾得個甩字 應該甩到見真皮<br />\n搞到隻手指有啲位好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係完全唔癢唔痛 不過甩皮既範圍好似愈甩愈多<br />\n甩完塊皮係新皮黎 唔會係又有皮硝 好平滑係比較紅咁<br />\n想問下係咪濕疹？因為以前我都有過濕疹<br />\n不過以前係勁痕又流水咁 而家又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經狂用潤膚都好似無咩用"},{"pid":"22b489a47c640168fd166be6a322b42d95784a30","tid":919192,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"乾燥甩皮姐"},{"pid":"e1fbfed6d929eb0b0b9aac59ad48e3e038ccd299","tid":919192,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b489a47c640168fd166be6a322b42d95784a30","tid":919192,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"乾燥甩皮姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"好大撻啊 又愈黎愈大咁 又紅又正精膚色咁<br />\n好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec1d0923890914f6dec46a215fe596d60309aec","tid":919192,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"保濕吧"},{"pid":"208bd85718ec87404017c557f3199c9f9cfb9556","tid":919192,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec1d0923890914f6dec46a215fe596d60309aec","tid":919192,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"保濕吧"},"citedBy":1,"r